headline: Can Bath & Body Works (BBWI) Leverage Disney Villains to Deepen Global Resonance and Brand Value?
summary: Bath & Body Works recently launched its Disney Villains Collection, introducing fragrances inspired by Maleficent and the Evil Queen, with early access for loyalty members and a global rollout both online and in stores starting September 3, 2025.
